xxl.core.indexStructures

Class MultiDiskBTree.Level2IndexEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.indexStructures.Tree.IndexEntry
      • xxl.core.indexStructures.ORTree.IndexEntry

  • Enclosing class:
    MultiDiskBTree

    public class MultiDiskBTree.Level2IndexEntry
extends ORTree.IndexEntry
    This class describes the normal index entries (i.e. the entries of the non-leaf nodes with level>1) of a MultiDiskBTree. Each index entry refers to a node which is the root of the subtree. We call this node the subnode of the index entry.
    See Also:
    ORTree.IndexEntry, MultiDiskBTree.Level1IndexEntry
